    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help <strong>x'Ar The Explorer</strong>, the lizard explorer find his place in the universe in this <i> space adventure demolition derby</i>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/ae058661a303f2c397c7edb3f83bc77b.poster.avif?t=1770903159\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/ae058661a303f2c397c7edb3f83bc77b.webm?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/ae058661a303f2c397c7edb3f83bc77b.mp4?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wanna be an explorer wannabe in a hostile space?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an ancient Jumpgate  and find a way to reactivate it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies have unique weapons and combat patterns</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/305672315b24b223cb7966d133933ad4.poster.avif?t=1770903159\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/305672315b24b223cb7966d133933ad4.webm?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/305672315b24b223cb7966d133933ad4.mp4?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 main quest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 optional side quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 Meaningful, fulfilling conversations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 000 words of dialogue (out of which 81 is swearing)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you're not busy fighting for your life, why not talk with <strong>several</strong> charming (and charmless) lizards inhabiting the Lekrad Orbital Platform and the nearby space to find out what they need and learn about your job, the sector, and yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/3c81375c2f1f27b3d3904ed823472fa2.poster.avif?t=1770903159\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/3c81375c2f1f27b3d3904ed823472fa2.webm?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/3c81375c2f1f27b3d3904ed823472fa2.mp4?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience through fighting and exploring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill tree with 8 upgrades, each with a unique cut-scene*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair your ship</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh no! Are the enemies coming in greater numbers and stronger? Adapt! Upgrade your spaceship's speed, agility, and damage, and unlock unique abilities (like impact-assisted asteroid redirection). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*cut-scenes may be skipped but it'll make the lizard sad :c (unless you're in a hurry)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/c31a0804b76255a975a5e0ad5e7d48cc.poster.avif?t=1770903159\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/c31a0804b76255a975a5e0ad5e7d48cc.webm?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/c31a0804b76255a975a5e0ad5e7d48cc.mp4?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly around and scan objects to gain experience and information</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scan the sector to find Points of Interest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scan the planet to map it and find anomalies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A small part of the entire universe is in your hands! Your ship is equipped with several scanners, which let you gain information about objects around you, as well as scan the sector to discover Points of Interest, which hold, well, interesting things. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware though! Sending out signals might attract some unwanted attention.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wow, you made it all the way down here? Have a Pizzové! Eat it while it's hot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/42a2ebe002323345ca332c4294dd3f4d.poster.avif?t=1770903159\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333760/extras/42a2ebe002323345ca332c4294dd3f4d.webm?t=1770903159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
